and, Ohio)|South]]''' Flyers (1904-2010)\n* Cleveland '''West''' Cowboys (1904\u201361)\n* Cleveland '''West Technical''' Warriors (1904\u201395)\n* Cleveland '''[[Whitney M. Young Gifted & Talented Leadership Academy|Whitney M. Young]]''' Warriors (2004-2018)\n\n==Eastern Buckeye Conference==\n{{Main|Eastern Buckeye Conference}}\n\n* '''[[Alliance High School (Ohio)|Alliance]]''' Aviators (2018-)\n* '''[[Canton South High School|Canton South]]''' Wildcats (2018-)\n* '''[[Carrollton High School (Carrollton, Ohio)|Carrollton]]''' Warriors (2018-)\n* Alliance '''[[Marlington High School|Marlington]]''' Dukes (2018-)\n* '''[[Minerva High School (Ohio)|Minerva]]''' Lions (2018-)\n* '''[[Salem High School (Ohio)|Salem]]''' Quakers (2018-)\n* Beloit '''[[West Branch High School|West Branch]]''' Warriors (2018-)\n\n==Eastern Ohio Athletic Conference==\nThe Eastern Ohio Athletic Conference league was formed after the Inter-Tri County League split into two separate conferences for the 2017\u201318 school year.\n\n* '''[[Columbiana High School|Columbiana]]''' Clippers (2017-)\n* Lisbon '''[[David Anderson High School|David Anderson]]''' Blue Devils (2017-)\n* '''[[East Palestine High School|East Palestine]]''' Bulldogs (2017-)\n* '''[[Leetonia High School|Leetonia]]''' Bears (2017-)\n* Salineville '''[[Southern Local High School (Salineville, Ohio)|Southern  Local]]''' Indians (2017-)\n* Hanoverton '''[[United High School (Ohio)|United]]''' Golden Eagles (2017-)\n* '''[[Wellsville High School (Ohio)|Wellsville]]''' Tigers (2017-)\n\n'''Former Members'''\n* '''[[Toronto Junior/Senior High School|Toronto]]''' Red Knights (2017-2019, concurrent with OVAC)\n\n==Federal League==\n{{Main|Federal League (OHSAA)}}\n* Canton '''[[Canton McKinley High School|McKinley]]''' Bulldogs<sup>1</sup> (2003\u2013)\n* Canton '''[[GlenOak High School|GlenOak]]''' Golden Eagles (1975\u2013)\n* '''[[Green High School (Green, Ohio)|Green]]''' Bulldogs (2015-)\n* Massillon '''[[Jackson High School (S