'' Indians (2019-)\n* '''[[Wellington High School (Wellington, Ohio)|Wellington]]''' Dukes (2019-)\n\n'''Second Version (Lorain County Conference, 1986-2005)\n* '''[[Avon High School (Avon, Ohio)|Avon]]''' Eagles (1986\u20132005, to West Shore)\n* Sheffield '''[[Brookside High School|Brookside]]''' Cardinals (1986\u20132005, to Patriot)\n* Lorain '''[[Clearview High School (Lorain, Ohio)|Clearview]]''' Clippers (1986\u20132005, to Patriot)\n* Oberlin '''[[Firelands High School (Oberlin, Ohio)|Firelands]]''' Falcons (1986\u20132005, to West Shore)\n* LaGrange '''[[Keystone High School (LaGrange, Ohio)|Keystone]]''' Wildcats (1986\u20132005, to Patriot)\n* '''[[Oberlin High School (Ohio)|Oberlin]]''' Indians (1986\u20132005, to Patriot)\n* '''[[Wellington High School (Wellington, Ohio)|Wellington]]''' Dukes (1986\u20132005, to Patriot)\n* Elyria '''West''' Wolverines (1986\u20131996, school closed, consolidated into Elyria)\n* Grafton '''[[Midview High School (Grafton, Ohio)|Midview]]''' Middies (1996\u20132005, to West SHore)\n\n'''First Version (Lorain County League, 1924\u201361)'''\n* '''[[Avon High School (Avon, Ohio)|Avon]]''' Eagles<sup>1</sup> (1924\u201361, to Inland)\n* '''[[Avon Lake High School|Avon Lake]]''' Shoremen (1924\u20131961, to Lakeland)\n* '''Belden''' Bees (1924\u201355, consolidated into Midview)\n* '''Brighton''' Bears (1924\u201352, consolidated into Wellington)\n* Sheffield '''[[Brookside High School|Brookside]]''' Cardinals<sup>1</sup> (1924\u201361, to Inland)\n* '''Brownhelm''' Bombers (1924\u201352, consolidated into Firelands)\n* Kipton '''Camden''' Knights (1924\u201352, consolidated into Firelands)\n* Columbia Station '''[[Columbia High School (Columbia Station, Ohio)|Columbia]]''' Raiders<sup>1</sup> (1924\u201361, to Inland)\n* Grafton '''Eaton''' Eels (1924\u201355, consolidated into Midview)\n* '''Grafton''' Comets (1924\u201355, consolidated into Midview)\n* '''Henrietta''' Hawks (1924\u201352, consolidated into Firelands)\n* '''LaGrange''' Wildcats (1924\u201359, consolidated into Keystone)\n* '''[[North Ridgeville]]''' Rangers (1924\u201327, to NOAL, 1933\u201361, to Lakeland)\n* '''Penfield''' Bombers (1924\u201359, consolidated into Keystone)\n* '''[[South Amherst High School|South Amherst]]''' Cavaliers<sup>1</sup> (1924\u201361, to Inland)\n* '''[[Wellington High School (Wellington, Ohio)|Wellington]]''' Dukes (1924\u201327, to NOAL)\n* Lorain '''[[Clearview High School (Lorain, Ohio)|Clearview]]''' Clippers (1928\u201338, to NOAL, 1947\u201353, to Lakeland)\n* Oberlin '''[[Firelands High School (Oberlin, Ohio)|Firelands]]''' Falcons<sup>1</sup> (1952\u201361, to Inland)\n* Grafton '''[[Midview High School (Grafton, Ohio)|Midview]]''' Middies (1955\u201361, to Lakeland)\n* Lagrange '''[[Keystone High School (LaGrange, Ohio)|Keystone]]''' Wildcats<sup>2</sup> (1959\u201361)\n\n# Concurrent with Inland Conference 1957\u201361.\n# Concurrent with Inland Conference 1959\u201361.\n\n'''Division Alignments'''\n\n{{Col-begin}}\n{{Col-break}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#ddd;\"| LCL Divisions 1924-38\n|-\n! Eastern\n! Western\n|-\n| Avon\n| Brighton\n|-\n| Avon Lake\n| Brownhelm\n|-\n| Belden\n| Camden\n|-\n| Brookside\n| Clearfield (1928\u201338)\n|-\n| Columbia\n| Henrietta\n|-\n| Eaton\n| LaGrange (1933\u201338)\n|-\n| Grafton\n| Oberlin (1924\u201337)\n|-\n| LaGrange (1928\u201333)\n| Penfield\n|-\n| North Ridgeville (1924\u201327, 1933-)\n| South Amherst\n|-\n| \n| Wellington (1924\u201327)\n|}\n\n{{Col-break}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! colspan=\"6\" style=\"background:#ddd;\"| LCL Divisions 1938-47\n|-\n! Northeast\n! Southeast\n! West\n|-\n| Avon\n| Belden\n| Brighton\n|-\n| Avon Lake\n| Columbia\n| Brownhelm\n|-\n| Brookside\n| Grafton\n| Camden\n|-\n| Eaton\n| LaGrange\n| Henrietta\n|-\n| North Ridgeville\n| Penfield\n| South Amherst\n|}\n\n{{col-end}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#ddd;\"| LCL Divisions 1947-55\n|