013/03/20/midview-to-join-swc-in-2015-16/ |title=Midview to join SWC in 2015-16 - Chronicle-Telegram |publisher=Chronicle.northcoastnow.com |date=2013-03-20 |accessdate=2014-03-24}}</ref>\n* Grafton '''[[Midview High School (Grafton, Ohio)|Midview]]''' Middies (2015-)\n* '''[[North Olmsted High School|North Olmsted]]''' Eagles (1954-)\n* '''[[North Ridgeville High School|North Ridgeville]]''' Rangers (2015-)\n* '''[[Olmsted Falls High School|Olmsted Falls]]''' Bulldogs (1954-)\n* Amherst '''[[Marion L. Steele High School|Marion L. Steele]]''' Comets (1947\u20131958 as Amherst, to Lakeland, 1986-)\n* '''[[Westlake High School (Ohio)|Westlake]]''' Demons (1954-)\n\n'''Former members''' \n* '''[[Berea High School|Berea]]''' Braves (1937\u20131950, to Greater Cleveland, 2005\u201313, consolidated into Berea-Midpark)\n* '''[[Oberlin High School (Ohio)|Oberlin]]''' Indians (1937\u20131964, to Lakeland)\n* '''[[Rocky River High School (Ohio)|Rocky River]]''' Pirates (1937\u20132005, to West Shore)\n* '''[[Fairview High School (Fairview Park, Ohio)|Fairview]]''' Warriors (1940\u20132005, to West Shore)\n* Lorain '''[[Clearview High School (Lorain, Ohio)|Clearview]]''' Clippers (1945\u20131954, to Lakeland)\n* '''[[Wellington High School (Wellington, Ohio)|Wellington]]''' Dukes (1945\u20131954, to Lakeland)\n* '''[[Medina High School (Medina, Ohio)|Medina]]''' Bees (1947\u20131986, to Pioneer)\n* '''Bay''' Rockets (1954\u20132005, to West Shore)\n* '''[[Brecksville-Broadview Heights High School|Brecksville-Broadview Heights]]''' Bees (2005-2015, to Suburban)\n* Middleburg Heights and Brook Park '''[[Midpark High School|Midpark]]''' Meteors (2005-2013, consolidated into Berea-Midpark)\n\n'''Future member''' \n* '''[[Elyria High School|Elyria]]''' Pioneers (2021-)\n\n==Steel Valley Conference==\nThe original SVC existed from 1949 to 2009. 2019 marks the start of the second incarnation of the Steel Valley Conference.\n* Youngstown '''[[Cardinal Mooney High School (Ohio)|Cardinal Mooney]]''' Cardinals (1970-2009, 2019-)\n* Youngstown '''[[Chaney High School|Chaney]]''' Cowboys (2003\u201309 [independent in football], 2019-)\n* Youngstown '''[[East High School (Youngstown, Ohio)|East]]''' Golden Bears (2007\u201309 [independent in football], 2019-)\n* Youngstown '''[[Ursuline High School (Youngstown, Ohio)|Ursuline]]''' Fighting Irish (1970-2009, 2019-)\n* '''Austintown-Fitch''' Falcons (1949-2003)\n* '''Girard''' Indians (1949\u201371)\n* '''Hubbard''' Eagles (1949\u201380)\n* Niles '''McKinley''' Red Dragons (1949\u201357, 1982\u201385)\n* Campbell '''Memorial''' Red Devils (1949\u201380)\n* '''Struthers''' Wildcats (1949\u201379)\n* Youngstown '''Boardman''' Spartans (1951-2003)\n* '''Brookfield''' Warriors (1959\u201368)\n* Warren '''Howland''' Tigers (1975\u201385)\n* Warren '''Western Reserve''' Raiders (1980\u201385)\n* Warren '''Warren G. Harding''' Presidents (1982\u201385, 1991-2009)\n* Warren '''John F. Kennedy''' Eagles (2003\u201309, Independent in football)\n* Youngstown '''Rayen''' Tigers (2003\u201307, no football, school closed)\n* Youngstown '''Wilson''' Presidents (2003\u201307, no football, school closed)\n\n==Suburban League==\n{{main|Suburban League (OHSAA)}}\n'''American Division'''\n* '''[[Aurora High School (Aurora, Ohio)|Aurora]]''' Greenmen (2015-)\n* '''[[Barberton High School, Ohio|Barberton]]''' Magics (2005-2011, 2015-)\n* '''[[Copley High School|Copley]]''' Indians (1949\u2013present)\n* Medina '''[[Highland High School (Medina County, Ohio)|Highland]]''' Hornets (1976\u2013)\n* '''[[Revere High School (Ohio)|Revere]]''' Minutemen (1957\u2013)\n* Kent '''[[Theodore Roosevelt High School (Kent, Ohio)|Roosevelt]]''' Rough Riders (2015-)\n* '''[[Tallmadge High School|Tallmadge]]''' Blue Devils (1990\u2013)\n\n'''National Division'''\n* '''[[Brecksville-Broadview Heights High School|Brecksville]]''' Bees (2015-)\n* '''[[Cuyahoga Falls High School|Cuyahoga Falls]]''' Black Tigers (2015- , to American Division 2021